<s> Dear friends, now, in Europe, is a great moment about accessibility: 1) in Italy we have the new Law 2) the Europea Plan "MINERVA" has published in november 2003 the official "Handbook for quality in cultural Web sites" [1].  </s>
<s> It is an important step into the european cultural life on the web, because the states members of UE will translate it in the own language and then will be applied.  </s>
<s> The goals about accessibility in this "Handbook " is is to follow the W3C WAI recommendations like primary condition, and we are very happy of this.  </s>
<s> I encourage to you to watch it and to say what of thoughts.  </s>
<s> Ciao to all, and Happy New Year!  </s>
